help please im and i think im pregnant and im scared out of my mind i started taking the pill a year ago to regulate my period but then two months ago i had sex with my boyfriend for the first time since then i havent gotten my period and im really scared what if i am pregnant how do i tell my parents and my boyfriend please i need help i dont want to have an abortion and im just afraid to find out in general i told my boyfriend and he freaked out how can i convince him to stay step calm down step calmly sit down with your parents tell them that you had sex and that you are afraid you may be pregnant tell your boyfriend that you might be pregnant and that you are going to a doctor to have a pregnancy test be prepared for him to leave you if you think it would help you stay calm and he is willing have him accompany you to the doctor's office step have them take you to see a doctor for a pregnancy test the home tests aren't as reliable step if you aren't pregnant talk to your boyfriend ask yourselves is having sex worth this stress and the risks are you willing to go through this again and maybe give up your plans for the future step if you are pregnant sit down with your parents and boyfriend and discuss your options if you cannot care for the child financially and emotionally put him or her up for adoption please do not abort the child he or she deserves to live just as much as you do step decide what you are going to do and stick with it best wishes for you and your family EastEnders Pregnancy Abortion debate Everwood Birth control Neighbours Prenatal diagnosis Abortion Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Psoriasis One Tree Hill (TV series) Roe v. Wade Teenage pregnancy Abortion in the United States History of As the World Turns (2000-present) Oral contraceptive Fertility awareness Sex and the City In vitro fertilisation Urinary incontinence Menstrual cycle My Parents are Aliens Knots Landing Phoebe Halliwell Miscarriage Hormone replacement therapy (trans) Kodocha Days of 